/backend/services/measure_engine/expression_parser.py

---

## REQUIREMENTS

Parse expressions like:

* SUM(sales)
* SUM(profit) / SUM(revenue)
* (SUM(profit) - SUM(cost)) / SUM(revenue)

---

## OUTPUT STRUCTURE (AST)

Example:

SUM(profit) / SUM(revenue)

→

{
"type": "binary",
"operator": "/",
"left": { "type": "agg", "func": "SUM", "field": "profit" },
"right": { "type": "agg", "func": "SUM", "field": "revenue" }
}

